# Production: full Fly (or other) API origin — HTTPS, no trailing slash, no /api.
# Example: https://student-expense-tracker-api.fly.dev
# GitHub Actions: same value as repository secret VITE_API_URL.
#
# Leave empty for local dev only (Vite proxies /api → localhost:8080).
VITE_API_URL=

# GitHub Pages project site base path; CI defaults to /<repo>/. Custom domain at / uses /.
# VITE_BASE_PATH=
